[
  {
    "sub_id3": "IEE3012  ",
    "scr_credit": 3.0,
    "sub_name": "智慧辨識檢測與應用",
    "sub_ename": "APPLICATIONS OF INTELLIGENT RECOGNITION AND OBJECTS DETECTION",
    "describe_ch": "本課程的目標在於讓學生了解智慧辨識、物件偵測軟硬體原理，完成小型專題實作。本課程主要軟體工具為 Matlab 及 Python。從運算思維開始，培養學生的邏輯思考的能力、自我學習及實作能力。",
    "describe_en": "This course aims to help students understand the basic concepts of intelligent recognition and objects detection, including the hardware implementations and software applications, and that enable students to complete the final project at the end of the semester. The main software tools of this course are Matlab and Python. This course will cultivate students' computational thinking, logical thinking ability, self-learning, and hands-on ability."
  }
]

