    "describe_en": "Providing the interactive opportunity establishes in the students and academic advisor, forms the good partnership. develops realizes student individual, the studies, the duty border goal, guarantees and achieves the student to study the achievement. Provides the profession plan and chooses the class consultation, and guides makes good use of the school each study resources and the service, obtains each kind of learning capability information and the opportunity, the auxiliary student establishes the complete learning experience and the course, lets the student individual study development, faces continues forever to study and the steps to success."
  }
]

[
  {
    "describe_ch": "班級活動及諮詢：培養學生責任感與凝聚班級向心力。",
    "describe_en": "Class Activities Operation and Advising: Cultivate students' responsibilities and enhance the sense of belonging.",
    "seq": 1,
    "levels": "C3 ,F3 "
  },
  {
    "describe_ch": "個人成長：協助同學發展核心軟技能及決策制訂能力，以及從各種學習經驗當中獲得綜合技能並能適時運用之。",
    "describe_en": "Personal growth: Develop core soft skills and decision-making. Be able to identify and communicate the transferable skills gained through your educational experience.",
    "seq": 2,
    "levels": "A3 ,B3 ,C3 ,D3 ,E3 ,F3 "
  },
  {
    "describe_ch": "資源應用：幫助同學分配與有效利用校園資源服務的技巧以達成學生目標。",
    "describe_en": "Resource identification: Develop skills in locating and effectively using information and resources that help you achieve your goals.",
