    "core": "U.系統思考：能面對複雜性、全面瞭解產生問題背後的結構、克服盲點、掌握見樹又見林的整體思考能力。",
    "core_en": "U.Systematic thinking:Be able to face complexity, fully understand the structure behind problems, overcome blind spots, and master the overall thinking ability of seeing both trees and forests."
  },
  {
    "core": "V.批判思考：能跳脫框架、從不同角度看問題、並能客觀分析不同觀點的利弊得失、能理性評估後做出客觀判斷。",
    "core_en": "V.Critical Thinking: Ability to jump out of the framework, look at issues from different angles, objectively analyze the pros and cons of different viewpoints, and make objective judgments after rational evaluation."
  },
  {
    "core": "W.創造力：能產生新思想、發現新價值、賦予事物獨特新穎意義，提出「不同而更好」或「新而有用」的想法。",
    "core_en": "W.Creativity: The ability to generate new ideas, discover new values, endow things with unique and novel meanings, and come up with \"different but better\" or \"new and useful\" ideas."
  },
  {
    "core": "X.協同合作：能尊重差異、強調互補、有效分工，整合不同背景專長，完成個人無法克服的專案。",
    "core_en": "X.Collaboration: Able to respect differences, emphasize complementarity, effectively divide labor, integrate expertise from different backgrounds, and complete projects that cannot be overcome by individuals."
  },
  {
    "core": "Y.自我管理(包括人際管理、情緒智商)：能認識自己、瞭解別人、控制衝動、管理自我情緒、想法及行為。",
    "core_en": "Y.Self-management (including interpersonal management, emotional intelligence): Know yourself, understand others, control impulses, manage your emotions, thoughts and behaviors."
  },
  {
    "core": "Z.複雜地問題解決：能分解問題、掌握工具、妥善分工、運用資源，逐一克服各項挑戰，勇於面對未知情境的能力。",
    "core_en": "Z.Complex problem solving: The ability to decompose problems, master tools, properly divide labor, use resources, overcome challenges one by one, and face unknown situations bravely."
  }
]

