  {
    "sub_id3": "MATH1005P",
    "scr_credit": 0.0,
    "sub_name": "微積分(一)實習",
    "sub_ename": "RECITATION OF CALCULUS (1)",
    "describe_ch": "內容包含函數極限，函數極限精確定義，利用極限定理求極限，連續性，導數，導函數，微分公式，三角函數之導數，連鎖法則，隱微分，高階導數，線性近似與微分量，極大和極小值，均值定理、導數與函數圖形之關係，無窮極限，水平漸近線，反導數，定積分，微積分基本定理，不定積分，代換法，曲線所圍之區域面積，函數平均值(積分均值定理)，自然對數函數，自然指數函數，一般對數與指數函數，反三角函數，不定型與L'Hospital's Rule。",
    "describe_en": "Topics include the Limit of a Function, the Precise Definition of a Limit, the Limit Laws, Continuity, Derivatives, the Derivative as a Function, Differentiation Formula, Derivatives of Trigonometric Functions, the Chain Rule, Implicit Differentiation, Higher Derivatives, Linear Approximation Maximun and Minimum Values, the Mean Value Theorem, the Shape of a Graph, Limits at Infinity, Antiderivatives, the Definite Integral, the Fundamental Theorem of Calculus, Indefinite Integrals, the Substitution Rule, Area between Curves, Average Values of a Function, the Natural Logarithmic Function, the Natural Exponential Function, General Logarithmic and Exponential Functions, Inverse Trigonometric Function, L'Hospital's Rule."
  }
]

[
  {
