    "describe_en": "The purpose of this course is to make the students, via the practical training, to learn the skills of programming and have the ability of programming. The course mainly includes  (1) the ability to define at an appropriately high level of abstraction the data structures and algorithms that needed, (2) the ability to devise alternative implementations of data structures, (3) the ability to employ different data structures in  algorithm design, and (4) the ability to analyze the time complexity of data structures' operation."
