    "describe_en": "This course will introduce the basic of object oriented design. Students will learn the basic concept of object orientation, object oriented principles, object-oriented design methods and object oriented programming skills. After this course, students should have the ability to apply object oriented characteristics, such as object encapsulation, inheritance and polymorphism to develop software programs."
  }
]

